            "title": "【異動板塊】出口航運碼頭股齊挫 申洲瀉近15% 美落實閞稅政策",
            "description": "<p>美國總統特朗普宣布向所有進口商品徵收10%的全面關稅，其中中國被開徵34%關稅，出口股顯著受壓，當中申洲(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02313' >02313</a>)沽壓顯著，一度大跌52.1元，大跌15.8%，新造52.7元，仍急瀉14.8%，成交有2.4億元。</p>\n<p>創科(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00669' >00669</a>)沽壓亦巨，一度低見85.55元，急瀉8.8%，新造85.75元，仍挫8.6%，成交有1.1億元。</p>\n<p>航運碼頭股亦向下，中遠海控(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01919' >01919</a>)挫4%；旗下東方海外(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00316' >00316</a>)跌2.6%；太平洋航運(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02343' >02343</a>)跌1.7%；海豐(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01308' >01308</a>)急跌6.3%；中遠海能(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01138' >01138</a>)降2.5%；中遠海運港口(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01199' >01199</a>)及招商局港口(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/00144' >00144</a>)各跌2.2%</p>\n<p>立即試用<a href=\"https://www.ejfq.com/home.htm?source=sapo9\" target=\"_blank\">EJFQ「信號」全方位股票分析系統</a>，運用100+選股條件篩選值博股！</p>\n<p> </p>   </div>\n        ",
